    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a very dependable choice for daily commuting or long trips. While there is some minor cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior consistent with its age, the overall presentation is clean and professional. All major mechanical systems are in solid working order, providing a great balance of performance and value for a discerning buyer.",
      "price": 33500.0,
