      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, offered in what can only be described as showroom-grade condition. This vehicle has been maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior environment that remains indistinguishable from its original factory state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, making this an ideal acquisition for the most discerning automotive enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of such caliber, representing the absolute zenith of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
